headline: Building Retail Resilience in New Delhi: Coca-Cola India's Commitment to Local Entrepreneurs
summary: Kirana stores are the backbone of India's consumer ecosystem. Recognizing their integral role, Coca-Cola India, along with its bottling partners - Moon Beverages Ltd. and Kandhari Global Beverages Private Ltd., is strengthening Delhi's retail network with advanced cooling infrastructure and digital tools to help thousands of local kirana owners grow their businesses.
